               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary by Cyriacus of Bəhənsa, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡, Prayer of the Blessed Virgin Mary at Golgotha, incomplete, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡, Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Calendar of the Apostles and Evangelists</summary>
